9. EPFO Data Detective

Target stakeholders: EPFO officers, data analysts, vigilance/compliance teams
Game format: Analytics and anomaly detection game

The player receives dashboards and datasets. They must detect suspicious patterns.

Possible missions:

Sudden drop in employee count
Repeated zero contribution
Unusual wage reporting
Same bank account for multiple members
High claim rejection pattern
Delayed settlements in a region
Grievance hotspots

Learning outcomes:

Builds data literacy among officers and supports AI/data analytics training.

Game mechanics:

Players use filters, charts, heatmaps, and anomaly flags. They must explain their findings and choose action.

Gamification:

Analyst score, false-positive penalty, early-warning badge, regional performance improvement score.
